name: Ultimate Island Trek
description: Embark on a thrilling adventure with the Ultimate Island Trek, a private jetski tour through the stunning Whitsunday Islands. Designed for solo riders with a spirit of adventure, this tour offers an exhilarating experience with the chance to encounter sea turtles, dugongs, and seasonal humpback whales. With the guidance of qualified tour guides, participants will enjoy informative commentary and breathtaking views, making it perfect for those seeking excitement and natural beauty.
includes:
All riding apparel including lifejackets, rash tops/thermal tops, wetsuit shorts, polarised sunglasses, riding hats and sunscreen
All photos of your tour provided free of charge on Facebook
Free courtesy bus pick up and drop off within Airlie Beach area
Thorough safety briefing and demonstrations provided by qualified tour guides
Fully supervised by one or two guides
highlights:
Jetski to a beautiful Whitsunday Island
Informative and entertaining commentary by qualified tour guide
Encounter sea turtles, dugongs, seabirds, and seasonal humpback whales
Free photos of your tour
Complimentary bus pick up and drop off within Airlie Beach
price_tiers: Solo Rider: A$495 per jetski | QLD Public Holiday surcharge: A$20 per jetski
ideal_for: Adventurous solo riders with above average fitness level and confidence in open waters
